{
  "stem": "5471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was after the October month when there came so many at once.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one wished-- knew about it, anytime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We still have contact with two and hear about a third.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were there to the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of our friends, here in Vaucluse, was there from October '42.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he stayed, stayed there with us, until the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That were the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was like a little town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So every department needed their own men to have it working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, my husband was allowed 30 people for the office.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That meant those 30 didn't have any chance to go on transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As long as he could keep them, those people were safe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everyone tried to, to get a job to be safe to stay in Holland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] from those 30 he started off with, when-- in '44, a lot of people had already been sent to Poland.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the camp occupation was less big as it had been.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He lost some of his people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He couldn't keep 30 anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was very hard because they were all counting on him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And whatever he tried, he couldn't keep them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
